      "text": "To configure Ruff in your project:\n\n1. Add Ruff as a dev dependency: `uv add --dev ruff`\n2. In `pyproject.toml` add:\n```toml\n[tool.ruff]\nline-length = 88\n\n[tool.ruff.lint]\nselect = [\"E\", \"F\", \"I\"]\n```\n3. Run checks: `uv run ruff check .`\n4. Auto-fix: `uv run ruff check --fix .`"
